{"tid":1225143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港台：林鄭強調自己初心不變　將持續向各界解說","createTime":"2019-06-15T06:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T09:15:28.000Z","uid":41404,"like":11,"dislike":643,"uniUserReply":116,"replies":[{"pid":"2f38c072ce67b22e4d654c1a085751ccf92e509c","tid":1225143,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:43:17.000Z","msg":"消息透露，政府決定暫緩修訂逃犯條例工作，行政長官林鄭月娥將於下午三時會見傳媒交代。林鄭月娥早上及中午分別在禮賓府會見行會成員及全體建制派議員會面，解釋最新決定。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，共有30多名建制派議員出席，會上林鄭月娥用了約15分鐘時間向議員講解，林鄭月娥強調，今次只是暫緩並非撤回，期間將繼續與各界溝通及解說，又說希望社會能平靜一下，不想見到有人再受傷。<br />\n<br />\n消息說，林鄭月娥在會上強調，自己初心不變，會再推修例，但沒有時間表，只是今個立法年度來不及再推，因為需要再作徹底解說。<br />\n<br />\n消息又說，林鄭月娥提到，近日網上很多短片及資料等都是全部誤導，但政府來不及反駁，所以認為要做更多解說工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463018-20190615.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463018-20190615.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=NKClBOrNcUwYLVyzdKWJdWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=6b712cf3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463018-20190615.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=49363b89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463018-20190615.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"0174cb4ff406c034a14b8b0dea1bdf2732c57df5","tid":1225143,"uid":41404,"like":31,"dislike":3,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4746244be939cf2e60a0defdadc9de0d1136bbf5","tid":1225143,"uid":126142,"like":523,"dislike":0,"score":523,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:44:59.000Z","msg":"你要玩火 可以繼續玩"},{"pid":"935ac57923f8dc68947d939259d02e4e3d678e14","tid":1225143,"uid":255105,"like":349,"dislike":1,"score":348,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:46:13.000Z","msg":"幾好，可以再企硬啲，警察國家既獨裁者係絕對唔可以向人民低頭"},{"pid":"db8876a86207bc1ef71d0138d5de46e539aaa8a7","tid":1225143,"uid":173814,"like":338,"dislike":0,"score":338,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:46:13.000Z","msg":"仲要強調唔撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你條八婆出親黎講野都係煽風點火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15bc43ed4ae7569a221e712f02e02e292f06484a","tid":1225143,"uid":54126,"like":209,"dislike":0,"score":209,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:46:24.000Z","msg":"柒婆講明<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">暫緩並非撤回</span></span> 仲未識死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab02095e3855dd0190312af52681150565a78230","tid":1225143,"uid":186152,"like":142,"dislike":2,"score":140,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:46:35.000Z","msg":"你夠膽再推 我夠膽再衝"},{"pid":"ce17ee0e85a7afad797e662d353264886aac2624","tid":1225143,"uid":13754,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:46:36.000Z","msg":"616重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 撤回惡法<br />\n2. 撤回暴動指控<br />\n3. 撤銷對手無寸鐵、和平示威者之起訴<br />\n<br />\n另加一個<br />\n撤銷官員、警察及損害香港民主人權者進入外國旅遊、工作或居留的權利"},{"pid":"bd8482d14d5b1e08b8399d541f32072d08f41dcf","tid":1225143,"uid":135313,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:46:41.000Z","msg":"林鄭你鍾意火上加油 星期日成存你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c82dbcc44d2c921eccfc72252683cb524ab9b3","tid":1225143,"uid":45376,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:46:47.000Z","msg":"平靜?<br />\n你縱容完黨衛隊